  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="white_box_shadow"><img src="/media/13077347/21518754184_8a7ce921df_k.jpg" alt="Ski Bundle Offers" data-udi="umb://media/6d8549dacfe54a2583684882295ffb58" /><br />
<p style="text-align: left;"><span class="location-text geolocation-title"><strong>Check out our fantastic Early Booking Offers for Fernie &amp; Kimberley</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/9516ae02f06047549f1709652a18a74d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9516ae02f06047549f1709652a18a74d}" title="Fernie">Fernie</a> offers world class skiing and excellent snow conditions.</li>
<li style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/0d3b1804f7e4412984147b3753069343" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0d3b1804f7e4412984147b3753069343}" title="Kimberley">Kimberley</a> is an up and coming resort with plenty of skiing. </li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span class="location-text geolocation-title"><strong>Fernie &amp; Kimberley Lift Pass Offer - Save up to 23%!</strong></span></p>
<p><em>Valid when you book any accommodation in Fernie or Kimberley for winter 19/20. [Not available on bookings between 21 Dec - 6 Jan &amp; 13 Feb - 24 Feb].</em></p>
<p><em><span class="location-text geolocation-title"><strong>Book by 15th November to save on your accommodation and lift pass!</strong></span></em></p>
</div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><strong>Accommodation Offers in Fernie &amp; Kimberley</strong></h2>
<p style="text-align: center;"> </p>
<div class="g4" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #dedede;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><br /><a data-udi="umb://document/9327428a613e4dafab45e278525a5bbf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9327428a613e4dafab45e278525a5bbf}" title="Lizard Creek Lodge &amp; Condos">Lizard Creek Lodge<br />Fernie</a></h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><img src="/media/13076466/lcl3-mark-shannon.jpg" alt="Caribou Lodge in Banff" data-udi="umb://media/e62aeb38256141be8ebad68eeb8da8a9" /></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">A long time favourite with Inghams guests, this hotel offers ski-in ski-out access and fantastic spa facilities.<br /><br /><strong>10% off accommodation</strong><strong><br /></strong><em>Not available on bookings between 25 Dec - 04 Jan &amp; 12 - 22 Feb</em></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/9327428a613e4dafab45e278525a5bbf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9327428a613e4dafab45e278525a5bbf}?0 style=" title="Lizard Creek Lodge &amp; Condos" data-anchor="?0 style="><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
<div class="g4" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #dedede;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><br /><a data-udi="umb://document/c10abdd393f840b59cf09f20860b1a02" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c10abdd393f840b59cf09f20860b1a02}" title="Fernie Slopeside Lodge">Fernie Slopeside Lodge</a><br /><a data-udi="umb://document/c10abdd393f840b59cf09f20860b1a02" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c10abdd393f840b59cf09f20860b1a02}" title="Fernie Slopeside Lodge">Fernie</a></h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><img src="/media/13077865/15906088376_591ac488b2_o.jpg" alt="Fairmont Banff Springs in Banff" data-udi="umb://media/b64a281019ad471f934a2e1832c9c61b" /></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Perfectly located in the centre of Fernie village with ski-in ski-out access and easy reach of bars &amp; restaurants.<br /><br /><strong>10% off accommodation<br /></strong><em>Not available on bookings between 25 Dec - 04 Jan &amp; 12 - 22 Feb</em></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/c10abdd393f840b59cf09f20860b1a02" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c10abdd393f840b59cf09f20860b1a02}" title="Fernie Slopeside Lodge"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
<div class="g4" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #dedede;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a name="backtotop"></a><br /><a data-udi="umb://document/bf517f66d1f34530ae3e34b6ce6be074" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bf517f66d1f34530ae3e34b6ce6be074}" title="Trickle Creek Lodge">Trickle Creek Lodge<br />Kimberley</a></h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><img src="/media/13078672/trickle-creek-lodge.jpeg" alt="Fairmont Chateau in Lake Louise" /></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">This lodge offers beautiful mountain-style settings with ski-in ski-out access just metres away from the chairlift.<br /><br /><strong>10% off accommodation<br /></strong><em>Not available on bookings between 25 Dec - 04 Jan &amp; 12 - 22 Feb</em></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/bf517f66d1f34530ae3e34b6ce6be074" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bf517f66d1f34530ae3e34b6ce6be074}" title="Trickle Creek Lodge"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div></div>
<div class="g12">
<p><strong style="font-size: small;">Terms and Conditions</strong></p>
<div style="font-size: small;">
<ul>
<li>Offers are subject to availability and may be withdrawn at any time</li>
<li>Date exclusions apply on accommodation and lift pass offers- see above</li>
<li>Percentage discount applies to accommodation price only - not flights</li>
<li>Offers applicable to new bookings made before 15 November 2019</li>
<li>When clicking through to book, the prices you see for hotels and lift passes already have these discounts applied</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>]]></bodyText>
